# Aedos frontend (Vite) — copy to .env.local for local dev.
# The backend API origin. Dev: the locally-running deploy backend.
# Prod: https://api.aspectresearch.org (the host the reverse proxy routes the
# API at — see deploy/Caddyfile; the SPA itself is served from
# https://aspectresearch.org, which is the CORS origin, NOT the API base).
VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:8000
